Name: LP
Description: Executing LP - counterparty to the trade.

Name: OutCome
Description: If the trade was WON or LOST.

Name: Side
Description: Trade side. "B” for buy and "S” for sell.

Name: TradeCcy
Description:
Denomination Currency for TradeQuantity and OrderQuantity. For example
    EUR.

Name: TradeTime
Description: TradeTime - Time (GMT) when the trade was filled

Name: ProductType
Description: Type of product traded. For example SPOT

Name: MissedByPIPS
Description: The difference between the AllInRate and the PriceShown expressed in pips

Name: MissedByUSDPM
Description: The difference between the AllInRate and the PriceShown expressed in USD per Mil
